<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Registro Exitoso</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f0f8ff; /* Azul claro */
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom right, #ffa500, #ffcc00); /* Naranja a amarillo */
            border: 2px solid #000000; /* Negro */
            border-radius: 10px;
            padding: 20px;
            width: 60%;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
        }

        .container h1 {
            color: #ffffff; /* Blanco */
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
        }

        .container p {
            color: #000000; /* Negro */
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            margin: 10px 0;
        }

        .container a {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 20px;
            padding: 10px 20px;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #ffffff; /* Blanco */
            background-color: #1e90ff; /* Azul */
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .container a:hover {
            background-color: #4682b4; /* Azul más oscuro */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>¡Registro Exitoso!</h1>
        <p>Tu cuenta ha sido creada satisfactoriamente.</p>
        <a href="inicioVenta.html">Volver al Inicio</a>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
